FacebookSelect
==============

Creates a facebook-style input.

Example
=======

Installation:

rake facebook_select:install

Usage in the view:

facebook_select('idea[tag_list]', suggested_tags_path(:format => 'js'), @suggested_tags, 'begin typing')

In the controller, have a function that returns the json for the input:

def suggested_tags
  respond_to do |wants|
    wants.js { render :inline => @suggested_tags.map { |tag| {:caption => tag, :value => tag} }.to_json }
  end
end


